24:55.216 --> 24:56.391
Mm.

24:56.521 --> 24:58.219
-[Lamar] Mm-hmm.
-[Slick slurps drink]

24:58.349 --> 25:00.438
[Lamar] Man, she got ass
for days, don't she?

25:00.569 --> 25:02.440
