of other shit, too, nigga.

25:02.571 --> 25:03.920
You know I could've
hooked you up, right, man?

25:04.051 --> 25:05.661
Yeah, you know,
beggars can't be picky.

25:05.791 --> 25:07.097
Plus, it's been two years,

25:07.228 --> 25:08.707
and I don't like
to overstep my boundaries.

25:08.838 --> 25:10.100
You can go on and keep those.
You can kill those, man.

25:10.231 --> 25:11.232
Thanks.

25:12.537 --> 25:15.018
Hey, man, so what you saying
about Meech?

25:15.149 --> 25:16.802
I heard he made
a play for Filmel.

25:16.933 --> 25:18.239
See, that was smooth.

25:18.369 --> 25:19.675
