from inside-out.

25:21.372 --> 25:23.635
Yeah, but see the thing is,
Filmel, man,

25:23.766 --> 25:25.681
he a soldier that pisses blood.

25:25.811 --> 25:27.770
Plus he's loyal as fuck
to Jay Mo.

25:27.901 --> 25:29.119
What's that about?

25:29.250 --> 25:30.512
[Slick] Him and Jay Mo went

25:30.642 --> 25:31.948
to fucking school together
back in the day.

25:32.079 --> 25:33.950
I'm pretty sure Mel told Meech

25:34.081 --> 25:35.430
to get on
with that smooth-talking shit.

25:35.560 --> 25:37.475
You know, smooth talk's
for pussies.

25:37.606 --> 25:38.824
Filmel, though,

25:38.955 --> 25:40.957
