25:45.570 --> 25:47.659
Mm.

25:47.790 --> 25:49.531
You might want to tighten up
your game with Monique,

25:49.661 --> 25:50.662
know what I mean?

25:50.793 --> 25:51.968
See, all that rough shit,

25:52.099 --> 25:53.143
you know,
it works for certain broads

25:53.274 --> 25:54.884
and all that.

25:55.015 --> 25:56.538
But, you know, sometimes,
you gotta be a little bit more,

25:56.668 --> 25:59.323
um, a little bit more refined,
you know what I'm saying?

25:59.454 --> 26:02.457
A'ight. P-M Suave.

26:02.587 --> 26:04.111
Lay it on me.

26:04.241 --> 26:06.026
